code: @Override protected ExecutorService createShardConsumersThreadPool(final String subtaskName) {     final ThreadFactory threadFactory = new ThreadFactoryBuilder().setNameFormat("KinesisShardConsumers-%d").build().     return Executors.newSingleThreadExecutor(threadFactory). }

@Override public void awaitTermination() throws InterruptedException {     try {         // Force this method to only exit by thread getting interrupted.         while (true) {             Thread.sleep(1000).         }     } catch (InterruptedException e) {         wasInterrupted = true.         throw e.     } }
